{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🐳 `langgraph build` 如何利用你的文件\n",
    "\n",
    "> **`langgraph build` 本质就是：根据 `langgraph.json` 找到你的 graph，然后自动帮你做 API + Docker 打包。**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 一、最核心文件：`langgraph.json`（真正的入口）\n",
    "\n",
    "这个文件是整个 build 的"指挥官" 👇\n",
    "\n",
    "```json\n",
    "{\n",
    "  \"graphs\": {\n",
    "    \"task_maistro\": \"./task_maistro.py:graph\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  \"env\": \"../../../.env\",\n",
    "  \"python_version\": \"3.11\",\n",
    "  \"dependencies\": [\n",
    "    \"../..\"\n",
    "  ]\n",
    "}\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 关键点解读：\n",
    "\n",
    "| 字段 | 含义 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| `\"./task_maistro.py:graph\"` | 文件：task_maistro.py，变量：graph |\n",
    "| `\"task_maistro\"` | API 路径变成 `/assistants/task_maistro` |\n",
    "| `\"env\": \"../../../.env\"` | 加载 OPENAI_API_KEY 等环境变量 |\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 **LangGraph build 就是从这里"抓住你的 agent"。**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 二、第二重要：`requirements.txt`\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "langgraph\n",
    "langchain-openai\n",
    "langchain-core\n",
    "...\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 build 时会 `pip install requirements.txt`\n",
    "\n",
    "> **这是你 runtime 依赖的来源**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 三、`task_maistro.py`（真正业务逻辑）\n",
    "\n",
    "定义了整个 agent system：\n",
    "\n",
    "| 部分 | 内容 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| graph 定义 | `builder = StateGraph(...)` → `graph = builder.compile()` |\n",
    "| nodes | task_mAIstro, update_todos, update_profile, update_instructions |\n",
    "| memory store | `store: BaseStore` / `InMemoryStore` |\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 build 完后，这个 graph 会被包装成 API 服务"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 四、`configuration.py`（运行时配置）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# configuration.py 的作用：从 API 请求中读取 configurable 参数\n",
    "# class Configuration:\n",
    "#     user_id\n",
    "#     todo_category\n",
    "#     task_maistro_role"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "比如 API 请求：\n",
    "```json\n",
    "{\"configurable\": {\"user_id\": \"123\"}}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 LangGraph API 会自动传进去"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 五、`start.sh`（仅用于 dev）\n",
    "\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "langgraph dev --port $PORT\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 作用：本地启动开发服务器\n",
    "\n",
    "⚠️ `langgraph build` **不用它**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 六、`docker-compose-example.yml`\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 只是示例部署文件\n",
    "\n",
    "⚠️ build 时 **不会自动用它**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 七、整个 Build 流程 🏗️\n",
    "\n",
    "| Step | 操作 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| 1️⃣ | 读取 `langgraph.json` → 找到 graph: task_maistro → task_maistro.py:graph |\n",
    "| 2️⃣ | 收集代码：task_maistro.py, configuration.py, 其他依赖 |\n",
    "| 3️⃣ | 安装依赖：`pip install requirements.txt` |\n",
    "| 4️⃣ | 生成 API server（FastAPI + /runs + /threads + /assistants）|\n",
    "| 5️⃣ | 构建 Docker 镜像：`docker build -t my-image .` |\n",
    "| 6️⃣ | 输出结果：Docker image: my-image |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 八、最终效果\n",
    "\n",
    "运行：\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "docker run my-image\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "你就得到一个 API 服务，可以这样调用：\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "POST /threads\n",
    "POST /runs\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "> **你的 graph 变成了"远程可调用 agent"** 🚀"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 九、文件角色总结\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "langgraph.json   → 告诉系统"入口在哪"\n",
    "requirements.txt → 告诉系统"依赖是什么"\n",
    "task_maistro.py  → 定义 agent 行为\n",
    "configuration.py → 定义 runtime 参数\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "合在一起：\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "graph code + config + dependencies\n",
    "↓\n",
    "langgraph build\n",
    "↓\n",
    "API service (Docker) 🐳\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 💡 最关键的一句话\n",
    "\n",
    "> **`langgraph build` 本质就是：根据 `langgraph.json` 找到你的 graph，然后自动帮你做 API + Docker 打包。**\n",
    "\n",
    "如果你想更深入，可以把 `langgraph build` 手动拆成 `FastAPI + graph + endpoints`，\n",
    "这样完全不用 LangGraph CLI 也能跑同样系统。🎯"
   ]
  }
 ],
